Class JDBMaterial

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBMaterial
public class JDBMaterial
extends java.lang.Object
JDBMaterial class is used to insert/update/delete records from the APP_MATERIAL table.

See Also:
JDBMaterialBatch, JDBMaterialLocation, JDBMaterialUom, JDBMaterialCustomerData, JDBMaterialType
